Maker Marial Maker (amụrụ n'ụbọchị mbụ n'ọnwa Julaị n'afọ 1997) bụ onye South Sudan na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agbachitere ma ọ bụ onye na-agba n'etiti Dandenong Thunder
Maker malitere ọrụ ya na Truganina Hornets nke asatọ nke Australia

Tupu oge 2016, ọ bịanyere aka na South Melbourne na mpaghara nke abụọ nke Australia. Tupu oge nke afọ 2018, Maker bịanyere aka na klọb nke atọ nke Australia Melbourne Victory Youth. Tupu oge 2019, ọ bịanyere aka na Port Melbourne Sharks na ọkwa nke abụọ nke Australia.

Tupu ọkara nke abụọ nke afọ 2020 na 1921, ọ bịanyere aka na otu egwuregwu nke anọ nke Spain Fuenlabrada Promesas. N'afọ 2021, Maker bịanyere aka na Atmosfera na ọkwa nke abụọ nke Lithuania. Tupu oge nke afọ 2022, ọ bịanyere aka na ụlọ ọrụ nke abụọ nke Australia Dandenong Thunder.
Ọ bụ nwa nwanne nne nke ndị egwuregwu basketball ọkachamara Thon Maker, Matur Maker, na Makur Maker.
